<BaseLayout title="About Our Construction Calculators" description="Learn how Construction Cost Calculator creates transparent, browser-based planning estimates." canonicalPath="/about/"><div class="container content-page"><span class="section-kicker">About the project</span><h1>Transparent Tools for Early Construction Planning</h1><p>Construction Cost Calculator provides straightforward tools for exploring quantities and early budgets. Every formula is explained, every cost assumption can be changed, and calculations happen locally in your browser.</p><h2>What these tools do</h2><p>They organize basic project assumptions into an itemized estimate. They are designed for initial comparisons, rough planning, and more productive conversations with contractors and design professionals.</p><h2>What these tools do not do</h2><p>They do not provide live market prices, local code analysis, engineering, architecture, bidding, appraisal, or financial advice. Real projects require detailed scope, local information, and qualified professional review.</p></div></BaseLayout>
